data.description: Welcome to this traditional classic beauty! 8708 Harrogate is located on a cul-de-sac in a quiet country-like setting, yet close to many amenities so you get the best of both worlds! You get almost an acre (what?) with a fenced back yard, a detached 2 car garage and a subtle carport for that extra vehicle. Over the detached garage you'll find an great sized room with it's own heating and cooling unit (not included in GLA).This room is perfect for an office, game room, craft/music room etc etc. Inside you'll find fresh paint throughout. Downstairs is the family room w/wood burning fireplace, a living room, separate dining room, kitchen and breakfast room. No carpet downstairs. Up the wooden stairs is a newly carpeted second floor with a generous sized master and 3 more bedrooms. A large deck out back overlooks the wooded fenced yard.
